ister for Forest and Environment, Prem Bahadur Ale, and NCP Provincial Chairperson Karna Bahadur Thapa, among others expressed their views.\n\nThe meeting decided to remove office-bearers including Sudurpaschim Province In-Charge of NCP Dahal-Nepal Group, Bhim Rawal, from the post, citing they carried out activities against the party\u2019s conduct.","title":"Wrong doers should be defeated: Minister Bhatta - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2021/06/154584/","video":[]}
